Your engagement on TikTok helps shape what you see. The more you interact, the more personalized your feeds will be. 

You can turn off personalized feeds at any time. This will change some parts of your experience, including changing For You to Popular, but it won’t affect ads personalization. You can turn personalized feeds back on any time to reverse these changes.
